# Ride Hailing Market: Global Industry Outlook, 2024-2030
## Introduction
The ride-hailing market size stood at USD 153.3 billion in 2023, and it is expected to reach USD 248.3 billion in 2030, with a compound annual growth rate of 6.1% during 2024–2030.

## Market Segmentation
The ride-hailing market can be segmented into:
* Vehicle Type: Economy, Executive, Luxury
* Commuting Pattern: Daily/Weekly, Monthly, Occasionally
* End User: Personal, Business

## Ride-Hailing Market Statistics
* 2023 Market Size: USD 153.3 Bn
* 2024 Market Size: USD 173.6 Bn
* 2030 Market Size: USD 248.3 Bn
* 2024-2030 CAGR: 6.1%
* Nature of Market: Consolidated

